OK...

The point of this map is to be a face paced gg map.  The catwalks and tunnels were made to help get off of awp and scout levels.  To also try to limit the time it takes to complete the rounds, the walls move and cause damage, the boxes break, the windows break and the barrels in the center blow up leaving a wide open playing field.  

This is the first map I made and I hope it is worth your time.  Please provide feedback.

This is a fairly large gungame map that is supposed to recreate diddy kong racing's Icicle pyramid battle arena. The recreation is a little off because I was doing it from memory, but it's pretty close. I did add an N64 logo in the middle to make it impossible to shoot across the bottom of the arena, making the top levels more accessible.  It is fairly large for a gungame map. 

Please provide feedback. If you upload it to your server or use it to make another map, I'd love to hear about it through a private message or by posting here.

This is my first map ever. I made it for our GG server. 
This is a dark map and has 32 spawn points.

This map contains 2 spawn sections on opposite ends of the main fighting area which is lowly lit. It also has 2 halls going down each side which are even less lit. 

There is a tall platform in the middle that overlooks most of the map.

This map should provide lots of knifing opportunities.

I was going for gameplay and quick games instead of "purdyness".....
perhaps the next one will have more eye candy

This is my first map to use custom textures. They were all created by me and are included in the map files themselves. I'm not sure if people will like the textures at all, but I don't feel like re-texturing this map so I'm just releasing it as is. It's mostly very close quarters so this map if a good rushing map. If you like it or hate it, please leave a comment anyway! :)

Btw, I don't know how to make a custom skybox so I just used a stock one. I hope it doesn't take away from the look too much.
